title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.23.08
description:
A LIVING NIGHTMARE:
   ---------------------
    A disturbing accusation?Charles&#039; life was ruined four years ago when his wife&#039;s ex, Kevin, accused him of molesting their children. Even after passing a lie detector, the accusations have continued, and Charles wants to clear his name for good. His wife Jessica, who&#039;s stood by his side through it all, also needs to know for sure. All three parents have thrown accusations back and forth, but today, Steve is finding out who&#039;s telling the truth, and who&#039;s lying!
